name: Courtesy Amount Recognition (CAR) updated from github
title: Transcribe number shown
instructions:
Transcribe text into image

  • Enter full amount shown with two digits, e.g. 103.00 or just full amount if the two digits missing , e.g.: 200,000
  • Do not enter the dollar sign
  • Text unreadable? Enter N/A in the text field

Watch the following video for more detailed instructions -
https://fasterap.s3.amazonaws.com/users/Demo/CARLAR.mp4
